    "The earliest application of deep learning models in AES tasks can be attributed to Taghipour and Ng (2016).",
    "This study introduced a neural network approach that predicts essay scores without the need for feature engineering.",
    "As it is shown in Fig. 1, the architecture utilizes CNN and LSTM to capture both local and global context information.",
    "Linear regression and sigmoid activation functions were used for the holistic score prediction.",
    "However, this work has certain limitations in terms of essay representation."
